<br>
Just leave this one on and you will know when your tank doesnt get hit anymore, and you have to recast the shield <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I rarely make use of the group DS. One situation would be in fast pulling groups with eventually several pullers (Velks upper spider camp for example).<br>
<br>
In every other situation, I only keep the shield on the MT, and watch the DS messages <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
